obfuscation: And O my darling , O my pet , Whatever else you may forget , In yonder isle beyond the sea , Do not forget you 've married me !
original:
And O my darling, O my pet,
                 Whatever else you may forget,
                 In yonder isle beyond the sea,
                 Do not forget you've married me!

obfuscation: Oh my darling , O my pet , etc .
original: Oh my darling, O my pet, etc.

obfuscation: Then away we go to an island fair That lies in a Southern sea : We know not where , and we do n't much care , Wherever that isle may be .
original:
Then away we go to an island fair
                      That lies in a Southern sea:
                 We know not where, and we don't much care,
                      Wherever that isle may be.

obfuscation: One , two , three , Haul !
original:
One, two, three,
                                Haul!

obfuscation: One , two , three , Haul !
original:
One, two, three,
                                Haul!

obfuscation: One , two , three , Haul !
original:
One, two, three,
                                Haul!

obfuscation: With a will !
original: With a will!

obfuscation: When the breezes are a-blowing The ship will be going , When they do n't we shall all stand still !
original:
When the breezes are a-blowing
            The ship will be going,
                 When they don't we shall all stand still!

obfuscation: Then away we go to an island fair , We know not where , and we do n't much care , Wherever that isle may be .
original:
Then away we go to an island fair,
            We know not where, and we don't much care,
                 Wherever that isle may be.

obfuscation: Away we go To a balmy isle , Where the roses blow All the winter while .
original:
Away we go
                           To a balmy isle,
                      Where the roses blow
                           All the winter while.

obfuscation: Then away we go to an island fair That lies in a Southern sea : Then away we go to an island fair , Then away , then away , then away !
original:
Then away we go to an island fair
                           That lies in a Southern sea:
                      Then away we go to an island fair,
                           Then away, then away, then away!

obfuscation: Of happiness the very pith In Barataria you may see : A monarchy that 's tempered with Republican Equality .
original:
Of happiness the very pith
                           In Barataria you may see:
            A monarchy that's tempered with
                           Republican Equality.

obfuscation: This form of government we find The beau ideal of its kind -- A despotism strict combined With absolute equality !
original:
This form of government we find
            The beau ideal of its kind--
            A despotism strict combined
 		With absolute equality!

obfuscation: Two kings , of undue pride bereft , Who act in perfect unity , Whom you can order right and left With absolute impunity .
original:
Two kings, of undue pride bereft,
                           Who act in perfect unity,
            Whom you can order right and left
                           With absolute impunity.

obfuscation: Who put their subjects at their ease By doing all they can to please !
original:
Who put their subjects at their ease
            By doing all they can to please!

obfuscation: And thus , to earn their bread-and-cheese , Seize every opportunity .
original:
And thus, to earn their bread-and-cheese,
                           Seize every opportunity.

obfuscation: Of happiness the very pith , etc .
original: Of happiness the very pith, etc.

obfuscation: Gentlemen , we are much obliged to you for your expressions of satisfaction and full feeling -- I say , we are much obliged to you for your expressions of satisfaction and good feeling .
original:
Gentlemen, we are much obliged to you for your
  expressions of satisfaction and good feeling--I say, we are much
  obliged to you for your expressions of satisfaction and good
  feeling.

obfuscation: We heard you .
original: We heard you.

obfuscation: We are delighted , at any time , to fall in with sentiments so charmingly expressed .
original: We are delighted, at any time, to fall in with sentiments so charmingly expressed.

obfuscation: That 's all right .
original: That's all right.

obfuscation: At the like time there is just one little grievance that we should like to ventilate .
original: At the same time there is just one little grievance that we should like to ventilate.

obfuscation: What ?
original: What?
